{"tid":907573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑港代理貨源 台灣幸福堂籲停飲港區產品","createTime":"2018-11-19T01:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T03:39:53.000Z","uid":102732,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa849027488ab3f3a3b159ae016843ca3b307dc","tid":907573,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A8%E6%BA%90-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E5%A0%82%E7%B1%B2%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81-150037117.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%25BA%2590-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25A0%2582%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E5%2593%2581-150037117.html&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d5a6d7cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A8%E6%BA%90-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E5%A0%82%E7%B1%B2%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%B2%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81-150037117.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eH_xnalOH5rM2hblfct0vA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/651f0bed473d7df1392049e9e65ac142\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FeH_xnalOH5rM2hblfct0vA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F651f0bed473d7df1392049e9e65ac142&h=e740776e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=52b180a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】黑糖珍珠奶茶近期在香港大熱，其中台灣幸福堂授權香港代理開設代理店後，雙方爭議不斷。台灣幸福堂日前在Facebook發出聲明，指不斷收到香港顧客對香港代理店產品的投訴，經派員視察後懷疑香港區的貨源，包括珍珠、茶葉及黑糖，可能不是來自台灣幸福堂，明言擔心有關食材可能引起食安問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣幸福堂指，總公司一直嚴格要求全球代理及加盟商，必須使用總公司提供的原材料，對有公司可能使用及提供並非來自台灣幸福堂的原材料，深感痛心，呼籲香港粉絲暫時不要飲用現在香港區的飲品，直至完成調查。該總公司亦展示多張由第三方提供的相片，顯示港台幸福堂所用的原材料包裝不同。"},{"pid":"9323b21ce525cdcd760fa635287e81d0bcf56ed1","tid":907573,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"咁咪改名叫元朗幸福堂"},{"pid":"175c583aa43232272c60bd58e800900caa7041fd","tid":907573,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9323b21ce525cdcd760fa635287e81d0bcf56ed1","tid":907573,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"咁咪改名叫元朗幸福堂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b0cff111c1f6c13d24b8e3b1128a5185416e6e","tid":907573,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"一次都未飲過"},{"pid":"a85ca3f4571eeea4375374b78ec6152c33487716","tid":907573,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真自家製"},{"pid":"1c6dfafd265efc38a98777c2b2458dfe6dfaf6fb","tid":907573,"uid":8671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"呢間野煩唔煩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74a2f8d3b7c332d88b62355a8f1d924272207b9","tid":907573,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85ca3f4571eeea4375374b78ec6152c33487716","tid":907573,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/